TY  - JOUR
T1  - The Aggregate Implications of Regional Business Cycles
AU  - Beraja, Martin
AU  - Hurst, Erik
AU  - Ospina, Juan
Y1  - 2019/11/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA14243
